952
01:16:02,017 --> 01:16:03,060
HOBBES:
Go right home. Go.

953
01:16:03,268 --> 01:16:04,937
TOBY: Okay, I will.
HOBBES: Run.

954
01:16:08,482 --> 01:16:10,442
