960
01:16:41,515 --> 01:16:42,557
I knew you'd come out.

961
01:16:42,766 --> 01:16:44,434
Put the gun on the ground!

962
01:16:44,685 --> 01:16:46,270
I know you, Hobbes.

963
01:16:46,520 --> 01:16:48,021
Set the gun down, sir.

964
01:16:48,230 --> 01:16:50,774
